<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>8007</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>11448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马上就要圣诞节了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天史密斯一家要去拿他们的圣诞树。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“杰伊、莎拉，快点儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们要出发了。”爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要去哪儿，爸爸？”杰伊问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要去圣诞树农场。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰伊和莎拉很兴奋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31540</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36075</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“耶，太好了！”他们欢呼道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36076</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41765</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到达农场时，他们看到那里有成千上万的圣诞树。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41766</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看这些树。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们被栽种成一列一列的。” 莎拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有很多种圣诞树。”爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59615</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那些是白松，这些是云杉。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>挑选一棵树不是件容易的事儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有些树太小。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66708</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有些树太大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有些树不够直。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这棵树怎么样？”杰伊指着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76888</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太细了，杰伊。”爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76889</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那棵树怎么样？”莎拉建议道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80489</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈不同意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太弯了，莎拉。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后妈妈找到了一棵高大，笔直的树。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我喜欢那棵树。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94740</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是一棵完美的圣诞树。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94741</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！我也喜欢它。”杰伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真漂亮。”莎拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102217</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸也同意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们把它砍倒吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109866</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用锯子切开了树干。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“树要倒了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“后退，杰伊。树要倒了。”妈妈提醒道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124749</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈和爸爸去付树钱，莎拉和杰伊喝着热苹果汁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124750</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>农场酿制美味的热苹果汁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，该回家了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“感谢你们。圣诞快乐！”农场主人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“圣诞快乐。”史密斯一家说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在停车场里，他们把新圣诞树捆在车顶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他们开车回家了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砍树只是完成了事情的一半。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157973</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>回到家，该是装饰圣诞树的时候了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157974</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把树上的雪扫掉。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164607</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来把树立起来。”爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164608</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸把树放在一个基座上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171405</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有这个基座，树就立不住。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171406</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我们可以装饰这棵树了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179810</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“首先我们要把这些灯打开。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179811</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莎拉确认所有的灯泡是否都正常。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸和杰伊把灯挂在树上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看这个。真漂亮。”莎拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个小铁兵是我的最爱。”杰伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，杰伊和莎拉。”妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们可以在树上挂一些亮片。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209013</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家挂好以后，莎拉很高兴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209014</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇，看上去很美。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212158</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>树基本上装饰好了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它看上去很不错，但是少了一样东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223022</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“星星！”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223023</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有星星装饰的圣诞树是不完整的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸举起杰伊，帮他把星星放在树顶上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236214</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在完美了！”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236215</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是最美的圣诞树了。”莎拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都非常赞同！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>